or manual:

mfrd            len

tape reader:
glitch remover  width, space
pulse pusher    width, offset
remap channels  track:chan, ...         live
edge sens       direction               live
deskew          margin                  live
unscatter find  -
unscatter       track:deskew, ...       live

nrz1:
crc/hpar marg.  min, max
mark marg.      min, max

pe:
preamble        min_len
postamble       min_len
mark            min_len


